{"commentv2": 1, "number": 41, "id": 1107800, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "strongarm91", "body": "The Burning Legion should have the Shadow Council reclaim Teron's body, resurrect him, and have him along with a group of warlocks, necrolytes, and Nathrezim (dreadlords) assault Lich King Bolvar Fordragon.  Teron Gorefiend should then become the new Lich King.  Teron would look awesome in the Helm of Domination with maybe some fel-green eyes.\r\n\r\nThe Burning Legion would then have the Lich King under their grasp.This should be done in the last expansion where we have to attempt to kill Sargeras.", "date": "2010-08-25T15:31:12-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
