{"commentv2": 1, "number": 43, "id": 1288645, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "743637", "body": "Just did this with a:\r\n\r\n85 Prot Paladin (me ilevel 340)\r\n85 Combat Rogue (avg ilevel: 355)\r\n\r\nNot listed here but he has a 10 minute enrage timer. I had to put out a constant 4.8k dps in order to beat the enrage timer, rogue put out 12k before dying to the debuff.\r\n\r\nHope this helps anyone who likes to do old content in small groups!", "date": "2011-01-11T06:05:54-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 44, "id": 1323425, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Choicecut", "body": "Solo'd as a protection paladin in a mix of Ret and Prot gear. With just one person it's a stand tank and spank encounter, Death Blossom is the only mechanic still present. Meeting the 10 minute enrage is the most difficult aspect of the fight.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1HPjG7-b0Jo", "date": "2011-02-06T00:43:33-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-02-06T15:40:58-06:00", 1, "Choicecut"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 45, "id": 1336662, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "myrddinde", "body": "Soloed as [u]Enhancement Shaman[/u].\n\nSoloing this fight is pretty easy these days as most abilities do not apply. All that remains is a tank and spank fight with lots of incoming damage. Teron did nearly 2500 dps to me, but if you use your cooldowns properly it is no problem at all, especialyl not after Supremus. Most of the Shadow Damage can be avoided by using Resistance Elixir and Drums of forgotten Kings.\nEven the enrage timer of 10 mintues is not a problem at all, the boss died in less than 3 minutes.\n\nEdit: [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PtB_vvLBf9A]added video here[/url].", "date": "2011-02-14T23:50:15-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-02-16T00:28:44-06:00", 1, "myrddinde"]}
