{"commentv2": 1, "number": 47, "id": 1467886, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Aerobear", "body": "\"I was the first, you know. For me, the wheel of death has spun many times...\"\r\nTeron, you damn Hipster!", "date": "2011-07-12T08:57:47-05:00", "rating": 99, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "His quotes are a direct reference to Lews Therin Telamon (the Dragon) from The Wheel Of Time series. Silly me just realized that today ;/", "creationdate": "2015-03-02T07:38:30-06:00", "id": 849791, "rating": 8, "commentid": 1467886, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "flepser", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
