{"commentv2": 1, "number": 54, "id": 1532646, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "IdTheDemon", "body": "Solo'd this a geared Demo Warlock. Took me a few tries. I had 2 nasty 2% wipes which broke my silly heart into pieces. You have to do 3.5 million damage in about 2 mins because you have a minute after he casts Shadow of Death on you to kill him. \r\n\r\nI pre potted, had the standard Warlock macro (Meta + Chalice + Demon soul), opened up with the fel guard then soul burned summoned the Fel Hunter. My Doomguard was doing work critting for 80k with his op Doombolts. Basically your typical Metamorphosis dps rotation in a raid.\r\n\r\nFunny thing was when I finally killed him, I had 1 second left on the debuff and it still went off. \r\n\r\n= (", "date": "2011-10-01T17:42:50-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 55, "id": 1551673, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Nobbel", "body": "A guide I made on how you can 3-man Black Temple.\r\n\r\nPart 0.5: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zk1gL_648pY&hd=1\r\nA tour around BT, showing the road\r\n\r\nPart 1: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1JcITK_zbgE&hd=1\r\nNaj'entus, Supremus and Shade of Akama\r\n\r\nPart 2: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ueHzTag9GBA&hd=1\r\nTeron Gorefiend, Gurtogg Bloodboil & Reliquary of Souls\r\n\r\nPart 3: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qyetuXk_0VA&hd=1\r\nShahraz, Illidari Countil & Illidan\r\n\r\nGood luck, I hope the guide helps in whatever you want to get out of BT :)\r\n\r\nNobbel the Noble, League of Champions\r\nTerokkar EU", "date": "2011-10-23T10:18:50-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 384, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
