{"commentv2": 1, "number": 60, "id": 1673746, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "jfmcghee", "body": "Quite possibly the easiest boss to solo for a feral druid. You literally sit in front of him and hit him for about 2 minutes. My health never dropped below 99%. Not tank spec'd, just dps in bear form.", "date": "2012-06-05T18:03:59-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Confirmed for feral bear... took more than 2 minutes but at ilvl 371 this was just a matter of not falling asleep at the wheel and popping cd's to maximize crits. I don't know it was b/c I was solo but fight went close to 5 min and I was never ghosted...", "creationdate": "2012-07-09T09:57:18-05:00", "id": 555521, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1673746, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "togahsisoka", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
