{"commentv2": 1, "number": 68, "id": 1843150, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Viserate", "body": "Well I'm not sure what happened recently, but for some reason I am unable to solo this guy with my WW Monk but could solo him with my Prot Warrior. My dps is about 2 1/2 times better on my Monk, but I die. It's very odd as this was a pretty straight forward fight on my warrior.", "date": "2013-04-14T16:24:12-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
