{"commentv2": 1, "number": 70, "id": 1877628, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Morbius", "body": "Soloed this with my 85 blood DK in 417 ilevel gear including Jade Forest greens and auction house blues.\n\nThe fight is just a tank and spank. If you have a pet or summon any temporary pets make sure you maintain aggro or he will cast [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=40251]Shadow of Death\n[/url] on you and cause a wipe.\n\nHere's  the video:\nhttp://youtu.be/QvPGKPCUxb0", "date": "2013-07-16T18:28:02-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-07-17T18:29:56-05:00", 1, "Morbius"]}
