{"commentv2": 1, "number": 72, "id": 1886870, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "269806", "body": "So i attempted to solo this on my holy pally killed warlord, supremus, then shade...but for some reason the door the gorefiends room isnt open\r\n\r\nbug?", "date": "2013-08-14T00:16:26-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "probably, it should always be open no matter what bosses you killed", "creationdate": "2013-08-25T18:03:32-05:00", "id": 687370, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1886870, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "imagine451", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I couldn't sleep so I decided to solo some old content. Had this same problem. Killed Warlord, Supremus, Shade, Reliquary, Bloodboil, came upstairs and Gorefiend's door is closed. I tried knocking. I tried \"Open Sesame\", and even \"Open Sezme!\" and nothing works. Anyone have any info on this just need something like a reset of the instance or what? I'm trying to farm the old T6 gear for my shaman, and his door is nothing but a setback! *snicker* But seriously. Anyone? EDIT: Found it. Turns out I was at the wrong door. This is what I get for doing this on no sleep. *le sigh*", "creationdate": "2013-09-04T10:15:19-05:00", "id": 689521, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1886870, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "mysgydid", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "At the Black Temple: Sanctuary of Shadows room, aside from the entrance you came into this floor, there are four entrances (including a closed door). Try to go around the floor counterclockwise (starting from the right side open room). And visit all bosses and kill them all. Then the left end door will eventually open for you.", "creationdate": "2014-06-18T04:21:37-05:00", "id": 751987, "rating": -2, "commentid": 1886870, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "midobu", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
