{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 80003, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "14240", "body": "He's at 58,70", "date": "2007-05-08T19:33:45-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "They changed the way he looks! He no longer has an orc 'form', but a human one, with a totally different face.  Looks pretty cool.  (oops, the picture posted above is his new look :p)", "creationdate": "2007-05-23T15:19:16-05:00", "id": 8031, "rating": 7, "commentid": 80003, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "40705", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He was given a human-body from Ner'zhul ^_^", "creationdate": "2007-08-16T20:42:35-05:00", "id": 13500, "rating": 8, "commentid": 80003, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "79966", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "actually, he got his human body from gul'dan. I'm reading one of the wow books and it says that gul'dan was making the death knights and he killed Teron gorefiend and re-animated him into a stormwind gaurd's body. so basically, ner'zhul didn't have anything to do with making what he is now.  P.S. he's a death knight. did you really expect him to give you flowers and chocolate for freeing him?", "creationdate": "2007-12-28T18:59:07-06:00", "id": 21927, "rating": 11, "commentid": 80003, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "zarocc", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Gul'dan did not kill Teron Gorefiend. Ogrim Doomhammer did. Gul'dan raised Teron Gorfiends soul and put it in a Human body which started the first Deathknights.", "creationdate": "2008-03-09T01:33:45-06:00", "id": 27811, "rating": 8, "commentid": 80003, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "108803", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It was not just any soldier; but a knight's body.  That's why they're called \"death [i]knights[/i]\" that's what it said in one quest series about him, that he probably was the only death knight that wasn't reanimated from a Paladin.  See the text in this quest http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10625", "creationdate": "2008-03-19T21:46:10-05:00", "id": 28689, "rating": 3, "commentid": 80003, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "129135", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 182185, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "gothnate", "body": "when i talked to him the first time just a few moments ago, he looked like an orc wearing robes...", "date": "2007-11-11T01:08:44-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 215033, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "53654", "body": "Death Knights are Orc Spirits placed in the corpses of Paladins.\r\n\r\nSo seeing Teron Gorefiend in spiritual form in SMV, he looks like an Orc.  Get it?", "date": "2008-01-08T14:27:42-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Yes Orc (Warlock) spirits, not Paladin corpses.  At the time that Gul'dan created the Death Knights, the newly formed Paladins of the Silver Hand hadn't fought the Horde yet and Stormwind didn't have Paladins.  It's funny that Arthas in the end of WC3TFT \"fuses\" with the Lich King, as the Lich King was made out of the orc shaman spirit of Ner'zhul and thus have parts of orc and human, like the original death knights, imho.", "creationdate": "2008-01-19T04:30:45-06:00", "id": 322867, "rating": 1, "commentid": 215033, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "32716", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[quote]Death Knights are Orc Spirits placed in the corpses of Paladins.[/quote]  Knights, actually. specifically, Azerothian knights who fought in the First War, which was before humans came up with the whole Paladin thing (it was the Lordaeronian knights in the Second War who were related to the Paladins).", "creationdate": "2008-12-11T01:08:34-06:00", "id": 63735, "rating": 5, "commentid": 215033, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arkham", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Maybe you never built a church in WC2, which upgraded the knights to paladins. (Teron Gorefiend and the death knights = WC2 = second war)", "creationdate": "2009-03-04T03:35:08-06:00", "id": 392097, "rating": 2, "commentid": 215033, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "294737", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I most definitely played Warcraft 2. The Knights in Warcraft 2 were [b]Lordaeronian[/b] knights, not Azerothian ones.  The Horde's Death Knights did show up in Tides of Darkness, but they were, in lore, initially created between Warcraft 1 and 2; they were ressurected from Azerothian Knights who died in the First War (Warcraft 1). They were not resurrected from the Lordaeronian Knights, who were the first Human Paladins; thus Horde Death Knights were resurrected specifically from knights and not from paladins.", "creationdate": "2010-02-01T00:53:14-06:00", "id": 146355, "rating": 5, "commentid": 215033, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arkham", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
